Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.09,0:00:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 米莉亚·伊尔·维尔克·科托雷托拉·图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.34,0:00:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为图兰的代理国王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在组织进行复国作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.93,0:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我手下的人给您添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说 图兰已经灭亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.69,0:00:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我在这
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.48,0:00:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家中枢与军队已被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.15,0:00:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也能算还没灭亡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因此 联邦不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.32,0:00:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你们的情况没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.99,0:00:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们已经和那两个空族人立下契约了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契约…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial}Touch and move
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.19,0:02:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出此等蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆她们在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.83,0:02:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装备只有一架Vespa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.83,0:02:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我们二人夺来十五艘难了些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠你了哦 吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.85,0:03:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 法姆你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉跟我们的船也没多大差异啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘死神西尔维厄斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.53,0:03:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Vespa与联邦的Shahas都不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里的Vanship呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米莉亚公主本人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}真人啊 真人！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}是图兰的白百合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那个 我说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐西尔维厄斯的感觉如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙要抢功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你 那色咪咪的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}别一直让公主站着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色咪咪的是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}椅子啊 椅子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找法姆的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}不是你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}是给客人用的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.56,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}没坏的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是快告诉我法姆在哪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的负责人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 给我说明一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战舰15艘怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如她所说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.25,0:04:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道鲸鱼的栖地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能让我联系卡尔塔法尔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.13,0:04:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃联系外界的想法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还怎么捕鲸？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内的东西随你使用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有舰长的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长着娃娃脸 还摆架子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.98,0:04:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你乱定契约
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来  只是西尔维厄斯一艘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么涨到十五艘了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是大势所趋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是骑虎难下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 死神吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别那么没出息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗盘座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很了解嘛 公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点常识还是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.43,0:05:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 做好准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.94,0:05:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从高度角与方位角推测 123…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在朝丘尔维斯望鲸哨西北2.4K
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东南偏南的小岛以43节移动中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往西走了那么远啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近的联邦基地有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏希亚基地在100哩范围内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较合适的目标是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乌鲁斯拉格纳或阿埃修玛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真幸运 竟然有两个候补目标
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.39,0:05:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然只通过目前位置就能判断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:54.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽的脑袋里装着百年来世界上所有的船哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百年？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有船的名字 所属
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还包括舰长和主要组员的档案哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于全部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这艘西尔维厄斯就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道九成就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以用下面的车间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个… 您是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是维修班长奥拉夫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只通过目前位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个孩子来说 挺能干的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.01,0:06:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们如果需要帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不妨碍工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请全力提供协助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意思的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.81,0:06:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么久没有联系 你竟然跑空族那去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exile落下来了 知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.82,0:06:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落在图兰的Exile的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是莉莉安娜公主 米莉亚的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦用Exile当武器了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉莉安娜公主被掳去联邦的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就有了神秘波动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.71,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说 难以与联邦达成和解？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看这件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的收藏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借我们一用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真狡猾啊 艾利欧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也随您差遣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要为了我捕鲸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 不乐意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图兰的事本是与你们无关的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.10,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆只是不愿见死不救罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我没有东西可报答你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.20,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我一无所有…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来一场Grand Race吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚夺回图兰的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起实现Grand Race吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在和平的天空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次我要将我的实力展现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 法姆你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要价真不低
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.27,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.73,0:08:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天不见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见啊 浪子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这里的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 西尔维厄斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.00,0:09:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一直不告诉我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.92,0:09:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.26,0:09:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 多提供些情报不是更好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不至于现在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.81,0:09:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦将在三天后宣布吞并图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞并？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家中枢与军队已被消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样也能算还没灭亡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.34,0:09:57.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主上瞭望台吹风去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:09:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完毕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这风真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.96,0:10:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.71,0:10:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡尔塔法尔没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.34,0:10:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和吉泽都会非常悲痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.93,0:10:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们最喜欢它了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果变成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会大哭一场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大吃一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.23,0:10:46.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大睡一觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.14,0:10:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后再次出发
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.94,0:10:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了组建新的卡尔塔法尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要米莉亚还在 图兰就不会亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就差领土和人民了 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.33,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 哪里还有领土
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西 哪里都可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家也行 船也行 什么都行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚你只要振作 大家都会聚过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 等好消息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料 冷却液 克劳迪亚正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃料罐检查完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.70,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度计
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导航调整
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.07,0:11:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操控装置正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动前检查 All Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Vespa基本一样 所…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.46,0:11:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.14,0:12:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.52,0:12:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会为你准备一支舰队的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.35,0:12:12.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次失败我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.61,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成立国家需要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府 人民与领土
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人民 这里也有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下领土了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说这艘船的弱点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.18,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我有事想拜托塔琪安娜舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然喜欢Cosplay
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺合身的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.25,0:13:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了人之后是领土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.46,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身衣服也没帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮不上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.71,0:13:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间正好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰糖葫芦似的真难看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时的船 强弱还都得看Tool的数量和颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 乌鲁斯拉格纳是有两根Tool来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,领土啊 领土
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定在某处的 在某处
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃顿饱饭睡个好觉真惬意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是饭菜难吃的话 活也干不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.38,0:13:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.51,0:14:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 吉泽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.80,0:14:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑的话会被怀疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有三根红色的Tool
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是纳尔维克司令部的离舰许可？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰相阁下也说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长的封地希拉兹很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.86,0:14:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能发生叛乱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希拉兹？ 没听过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色狼舰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致维多利亚斯王子号舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔斯的书信如下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.13,0:14:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致艾伦斯特·基尔斯·林德曼阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令堂请您急速返乡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.68,0:14:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 母亲大人她？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命你明早务必赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天早晨！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.35,0:14:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王… 王子速度很慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条冰糖鲸鱼的确非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长 似乎准备了一艘快船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.65,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等片刻 母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.90,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引擎舱完成压制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.26,0:15:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰首炮塔 压制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.76,0:15:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后部瞭望塔 压制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.18,0:15:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上部甲板及全部炮塔 压制
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵不血刃 就压制了这么一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有完善的准备和情报 捕鲸等于成功了九成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是胆量与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.78,0:15:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有美貌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉泽尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您务必助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救濒临灭亡的图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个房间让给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.43,0:16:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明听说「这身打扮能让任何男人心动」的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.53,0:16:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九点钟方向有引擎声
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战列舰级别的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员进入备战状态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明战列舰接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始无音航行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左转15度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无音航行 左转15度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告目标舰位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.37,0:16:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前距离2.5
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以相对速度80节接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测员 尽快目视索敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员备战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs35}重复 全员备战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五分队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备白刃战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.39,0:17:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.81,0:17:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏起来吧 很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米 米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从接近中的船传来声音信号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是奥拉夫 作战成功
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.88,0:17:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解除战备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.84,0:17:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近中的船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是空族夺来的战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了吗 泰迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:17:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是图兰国王代理 第二王女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚·伊尔·维尔克·科托雷托拉·图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿德斯联邦无视Grand Lake上的神圣和平交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残忍地蹂躏了图兰的国土
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我王都变为废墟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.38,0:18:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不止如此 他们大展侵略之手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.60,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在其残暴的攻势下周边各国也危机重重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了对抗阿德斯的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我身为热爱自由与和平的图兰国民的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓定会与其抗争到底
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并在此宣布新图兰王国成立
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,征服者已被打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.95,0:18:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阔别已久的古老的哥尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次回到了它真正主人的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断遭受迫害的子民啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加团结起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.72,0:18:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 将一切夺回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此 向历史与祖先
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起誓并宣布合并图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一个星球 同一个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.12,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同一个民族 是我等的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣光同在 奥古斯塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房 浴室与我的卧室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为图兰流亡政府的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并要求每日提供食物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上是对方的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很有意思的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就出师有名了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会陷入与阿德斯联邦的正面交锋哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你说的和平很难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.73,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无法对她们见死不救吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一只迷路的小鸟来说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.11,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得还算不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微… 让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.24,0:20:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}别推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得漂亮 法姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:00.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.88,0:21:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没… 没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是为了复兴图兰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}法姆 你笑得太过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.93,0:21:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法姆 爆笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝贺流亡政府成立
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.82,0:21:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.82,0:21:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 真丢人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我能做的只有这些
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.80,0:21:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我真的能将图兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里是米莉亚真真正正
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.26,0:21:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭借自己的力量得来的领土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.94,0:21:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张桌子就是值得纪念的第一方领土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是整艘西尔维厄斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.23,0:22:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再然后夺回图兰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.29,0:22:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间磨磨蹭蹭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.83,0:22:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Race还在等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.17,0:22:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
